import React, {useState} from 'react'; import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'; import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav'; import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar'; import NavDropdown from 'react-bootstrap/NavDropdown'; import { Link, useLocation } from 'react-router-dom'; import './Menu.css'; export default function Menu() { const [isActive, setActive] = useState( { home: true, letter: false, financial: false, achieving: false, }); const homeClassName='nav-link ' + (isActive.home ? 'active' : ''); const letterClassName='nav-link ' + (isActive.letter ? 'active' : ''); const location = useLocation(); switch(location.path) { case '/about': console.log('success'); setActive({home: false, letter: true, financial: false, achieving: false}); break; } return (
setActive({home: true, letter: false, financial: false, achieving: false})} bsPrefix={homeClassName} to='/'>
> 01 Home
setActive({home: false, letter: true, financial: false, achieving: false})} bsPrefix={letterClassName}> 02 Letter to Our Shareholders 03 FY22 Financial Highlights
04 Achieving Commitments and Delivering Enduring Value 05 Expertise and Technology for
Mission and Enterprise Customers 06 Positioned for the Future of
National Security 07 UK Summary 08 Board of Directors 09 Additional Information
); }
